original_title: The 2nd Photobook H:OUR - TOMORROW X TOGETHER (TXT)
overview: H:Our is the second photobook of TOMORROW X TOGETHER (TXT) after their debut photobook of the same name came out on January 28, 2020. The newest one was released on September 23, 2020.  The photo shoot for the photobook took place in Jeju island in Korea.
title: The 2nd Photobook H:OUR - TOMORROW X TOGETHER (TXT)
